headline: GE Aerospace Contracts And Partnerships Put Valuation Expectations In Focus
summary: GE Aerospace, part of General Electric (NYSE:GE), is working with Kratos Defense on the U.S. Air Force GEK1500 engine program for unmanned aerial systems. GE is supporting Starfighters Space on its STARLAUNCH I program, which recently reached a program milestone using GE Aerospace propulsion expertise.
